name: Obstacle Course 3D
description:
A simple 3D obstacle course,

Try to get from start point to finish point without touching the objects.

CONTROLS: WASD and Arrow Keys If you want to quit the game press Alt + F4

This project is made for learning purposes, it is still under development.

Hope you enjoy!

Will be updating.

GitHub link for this project: https://github.com/Scientist8/Obstacle_Course_3D.game
